avRegistration.loginHeader: Login to your Agora Voting account
avRegistration.helpRegisterForm: To be able to vote, you need to register first. Some fields are required, so please look carefully at the help information.
avRegistration.helpAdminRegisterForm: To be able to create elections, you need to register first. Please look carefully at the help information.
avRegistration.fillValidFormText: To be able to send the form, please fill correctly first all the fields.
avRegistration.invalidRegisterData: No ha sido posible registrarte con los datos aportados. Lo más probable es que ya estés registrado, accede usando tus credenciales pinchando aquí. También puede que el periodo de votación haya finalizado. Comprueba todo lo anterior, y en caso de que sigas teniendo problemas, revisa tus datos, o ponte en contacto con los administradores de la votación,
avRegistration.invalidRegisterDNI: No ha sido posible registrarte con los datos aportados. Has insertado un número de DNI inválido. Por favor, revísalo.
avRegistration.codeHelp: Please use the last code we have sent to your phone. The code will have 8 alphanumeric characters.
avRegistration.noCodeReceivedQuestion: Did not receive your code yet?
avRegistration.telInvalid: Invalid telephone number. Example of valid number: +34666666666
avRegistration.telHelp: Only numbers, with no spaces or hyphens. For numbers outside Spain, use the country prefix, for example +34.
avRegistration.errorSendingAuthCode: Error sending the code. Please review that you wrote correctly your phone, or maybe you sent the code too many times. If the problem persist, contact with the organization.
avRegistration.fewMinutes: It only takes a few minutes
avRegistration.helpAlreadyRegisteredForm: Maybe you are already registered and what you really need is to authenticate.
avRegistration.loginHere: Access using my credentials, I have already registered before
avRegistration.dniHelp: Specify a valid  DNI/NIE. Examples: 12343567R or X01234356R
